<p class="paragraph-text">From heart-wrenching ballads like &#x27;Right Here Waiting&#x27; to upbeat anthems like &#x27;Satisfied&#x27;, each song in this list showcases Marx&#x27;s talent for crafting melodious hits that are both emotive and enduring.</p><ul><li><a href="/news/music/richard-marx-interview-luther-vandross-video/"><strong>Richard Marx recalls emotional story behind co-writing &#x27;Dance with My Father&#x27; with Luther Vandross</strong></a></li><li><a href="/news/music/richard-marx-olivia-newton-john-friendship/"><strong>Richard Marx was &quot;madly in love&quot; with Olivia Newton-John before they worked together</strong></a></li></ul><p class="paragraph-text">Join us as we journey through the highs and poignant moments of Richard Marx&#x27;s musical legacy, celebrating the songs that have defined his career.</p><p class="paragraph-text">Note: We&#x27;re sticking to his solo hits, rather than the many songs he wrote for artists, such as <a href="/features/the-story-of/dance-with-my-father-lyrics-meaning-facts-video/">&#x27;Dance with My Father&#x27;</a> by <a href="/artists/luther-vandross/facts-age-partner-songs-death/">Luther Vandross</a>.</p><div data-openweb-ad data-row="1" data-column="1"></div>
