    <a href="/news/entertainment/grease-john-travolta-audition-danny/" ><div class="img_wrapper"><img
     loading="lazy"
    src="https://imgs.smoothradio.com/images/647359?width=105&amp;crop=1_1&amp;format=webp&amp;signature=jbCKlBRG9i1rzLlpuW6iAEA7rcE="
    width="105"
    height="105"
    alt="John Travolta in the 1970s"
    srcset="https://imgs.smoothradio.com/images/647359?width=105&amp;crop=1_1&amp;format=webp&amp;signature=jbCKlBRG9i1rzLlpuW6iAEA7rcE= 105w"
    sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 105px, (max-width: 1024px) and (min-width: 485px) 105px, 100vw"
/></div><h3><span class="ellipsis">Grease: How John Travolta's "unfocused" audition initially got him cast as another</span><span class="truncated"> character</span></h3></a>
    <div class="card__extra-content">
